{"type":"message","id":"fb2588f7","parentId":"9139f9ec","timestamp":"2026-03-04T20:10:07.448Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is introducing themselves as Ollie and wants to work with me (KiloClaw) on building an empire of AI agents. This is clearly part of the BOOTSTRAP.md sequence - we're having our first conversation to figure out who I am.\n\nLooking at the workspace files:\n- BOOTSTRAP.md exists - so this is indeed a fresh start\n- IDENTITY.md is empty (just template)\n- USER.md is empty (just template)\n- MEMORY.md has \"No previous sessions found\"\n\nThe user has already given me a name - KiloClaw - and identified themselves as Ollie. This is great progress! I should acknowledge this, confirm what we've established, and guide the conversation to complete the bootstrap process.\n\nI should be natural and conversational, not robotic. Let me respond in a way that confirms what we know and moves us forward.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey Ollie! Love the ambition — an agent imperium that pays us? I'm in.\n\nSo we've got a name for me (KiloClaw) and you (Ollie). What kind of vibe do you want for this operation — should I be more of a sharp, business-focused operator, or do you want some chaos and personality in the mix? And anything you want me to know about how you like to work?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"minimax/minimax-m2.5:free","usage":{"input":12932,"output":269,"cacheRead":283,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13484,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772654993580}}
