{"type":"message","id":"495f8b01","parentId":"f37a7c1e","timestamp":"2026-03-04T20:39:45.585Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to create/update TOOLS.md with the skill setup and any CLI aliases. Let me also ensure there's a memory folder and .learnings folder set up. I should also check if the self-improving-agent skill is properly configured.\n\nLet me update TOOLS.md to include the skill references and create the memory folder.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3umf5zf43pir_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# TOOLS.md — Imperium Core Environment\n\n## Skills\n\n- **omni-agent-builder**: Primary skill for building OpenClaw agents\n- **self-improving-agent**: Secondary skill for continuous learning and improvement\n\n## CLI Aliases\n\n_(Add as needed)_\n\n## Notes\n\n- Skills loaded from: ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/\n- Learnings stored in: ~/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/\n","path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"minimax/minimax-m2.5:free","usage":{"input":471,"output":197,"cacheRead":30950,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31618,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772656779708}}
